Title: An Act Changing the Name of the Antique General Hospital in the Municipality of San Jose, Province of Antique, to Angel Salazar Memorial General Hospital
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 89
An Act Changing the Name of the Antique General Hospital in the Municipality of San Jose, Province of Antique, to Angel Salazar Memorial General Hospital
Section 1. The name of the Antique General Hospital in the Municipality of San Jose, Province of Antique, is hereby changed to Angel Salazar Memorial General Hospital.
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: October 14, 1980
